cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.SI 

This paper is likely to belong to the sub-category of cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it deals with the error landscape of deep neural networks. It could also belong to cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as it studies the behavior of neural networks. Additionally, since the paper discusses the optimization of neural networks, it could be categorized under cs.CV (Computer Vision) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, since the paper presents conditions for global optimality, it could also be classified under cs.SI (Social and Information Networks).
